name: Sheena
description:
'''Sheena Mae Manuel Catacutan''' (born May 9, 2004), known mononymously as '''Sheena''', is a Filipino singer and dancer under [[Star Music]]. She is the youngest member, main dancer, and one of the sub vocalists of the Filipino girl group [[Bini (group)|Bini]]. She was a housemate on ''[[Pinoy Big Brother: Otso]]'' (2018) with Gwen Apuli.

In 2025, she portrayed herself in an episode of the anthology series ''[[Maalaala Mo Kaya]]'', which depicted her life story. She was also nominated as Viral [[TikTok]] of the Year category at VP Choice Awards 2025.
